CHARMEE CHARMIE

Charmee is a term coined for mobile (non-player) characters that are
either charmed, or otherwise controlled by PC (player characters).

See also:  ORDER

**NOTE:  An important change to the charmee system - You can only
have as many charmee's as your charisma-bonus (Stat bonus is equal
to (Stat-10)/2 , i.e. 18 charisma = (18-10)/2 = 4).  Any amount
order followers charmee's above that value have a high chance of rebelling and
attacking the caster.

***Another note:  Despite charisma-bonus, you can have at least one
charmee.

See also:  DISMISS
