Clan popularity is a measure of how popular your clan is around the MUD.  It is
affected by using diplomacy skills on certain mobs within each area.

All clans start at 0% popularity in all zones, and can increase the popularity
in a zone by using the murmur, propaganda and lobby skills in that zone.

When popularity in a zone reaches 75%, the zone may be claimed for the clan.

When members of other clans use diplomacy skills in the zone, your own clan's
popularity may be affected, but the claim will remain until the zone is claimed
by another clan.

